@DATABASE "Falcon Patrol 2"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - F - Falcon Patrol 2"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - F
                   ====================================

                              Falcon Patrol 2
                              ===============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(45363,255)"}          455363,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(40554,0)"}          40554,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
